This paper is primarily focused on person re-identification (Re-ID) using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses ranking optimization and evaluation metrics, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses security and privacy concerns related to video surveillance, which could fall under the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
